 dano patrimonial ou extrapatrimonial, nexo de causalidade, e \n4. Excludentes de Responsabilidade\nAs principais excludentes sao: culpa exclusiva da vitima, fato de terceiro, caso fortuito e forca maior, legitima defesa, e\n5. Dano Moral\nO dano moral e a lesao aos direitos da personalidade. A Constituicao Federal de 1988 consagrou expressamente a po", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 883, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}}, "docstore/ref_doc_info": {"f9ba9037-c813-48a4-9860-c8170cbb7a9c": {"node_ids": ["9011b25e-f173-4f6c-af8c-031655c72190"], "metadata": {"doc_id": "cb054a25-3b84-444f-917d-35b5fd5d9f67", "autor": "Carlos Roberto Goncalves", "author": "Carlos Roberto Goncalves", "arquivo": "test_legal_book.pdf", "title": "Curso de Direito Civil Brasileiro", "ano": 2018, "year": 2018, "edition": "", "materia": "Direito Civil", "legal_subject": "Direito Civil", "legal_institute": "", "hash": "e256c7daf73c75e31af1b26fd63d02931c0dee1f34a670e586d0389c9a451493", "caminho": "/app/backend/data/uploads/test_legal_book.pdf"}}}, "docstore/metadata": {"9011b25e-f173-4f6c-af8c-031655c72190": {"doc_hash": "c4a93f12b77639354da28144e1c8f359c5e62eea9ae141c660a9f70a3b3fb6d9", "ref_doc_id": "f9ba9037-c813-48a4-9860-c8170cbb7a9c"}, "f9ba9037-c813-48a4-9860-c8170cbb7a9c": {"doc_hash": "a1e0be88531c4265179ddd392a11fa9e69b185287445c553178090cf11efe6a2"}}}